name: Fédération Cynologique Internationale - European Section
bossPosition: President of the Board of FCI Europe
goal: Founded in 1911, the FCI – European Section - represents the Fédération Cynologique Internationale (FCI – World Canine Federation). Our role is to further the breeding and keeping of healthy pedigree dogs.
interests: Agriculture and Rural Development, Public Health
euInitiatives: All initiatives related to animal welfare in particular companion animals (transport, health, trade)
